item.title: Fame
item.description: Send us a text Katie and special guest Jahleel(!) audition at a Performing Arts High School as they re-watch the 80's hit: Fame! #We'reGonnaLiveForever! Come along as we follow high school students as they journey through auditioning into their school and then surviving the next four years. And we do mean SURVIVING, as we encounter lots of real world hardships such as: drug abuse, rejections, death, grief, identity issues, jealously, coming out, abortion, racism, classism, sexual abuse...
